reviewText: Not good I expected so much more.
Perfect for that American hating zealot in your life!

Remember when Rosie was really funny? Well, if not, here it 'tis! I just wish she could've stayed this funny.
You'll enjoy this young and funny Rosie alright! A blast from the past!
This was a gift for a Rosie fan friend of mine.  She enjoyed the DVD and is still after me to watch is sometime with her.

OK collection of some of Rosie O'Donnell's stand-up routines, but the routines are not complete as far as I can tell.  Also there are some routines that I remember seeing on cable over twenty years ago that were not included.  This collection is alright but not ideal.
I've always been a fan of Rosie - and was excited to see some of her old stand up - I wish she would go back on tour - video was too short - but fun!
This is true stand up work from her early years collected from different clubs.  Hilarious!
